# Auto-push for this repo

After completing any meaningful file changes in this project:

1. Stage and commit with a concise message (unless the user asked not to).
2. Push to `origin` (`git push -u origin HEAD`) without waiting to be asked.
3. Do not force-push. Do not amend commits already pushed.
4. Skip committing secrets (`.env`, credentials).
